{"tid":1588973,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"政府強烈譴責示威者多區破壞將依法追究","createTime":"2019-09-23T05:14:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T05:26:31.000Z","uid":13289,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"14ef73e17b55d520fd8f0520bf5334dbba8a802a","tid":1588973,"uid":13289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T05:14:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/saPPrex.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsaPPrex.jpg&h=cfedbdde&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【Now新聞台】政府強烈譴責示威者周日在多區破壞。<br />\n<br />\n政府發言人表示激進示威者分別在沙田及旺角堵路、縱火及投擲汽油彈，危害市民安全，又在多個商場破壞設施，滋擾商戶，影響市民生活，漠視其他人的權利，批評他們行為極為自私。又指他們破壞多個港鐵站設施，干擾列車運作，影響港鐵服務，有人更用不同方式侮辱國旗，挑戰國家主權，政府強烈譴責，強調警方會依法追究。"},{"pid":"854f3b395b2604d2342b4ed01f3c79a321af40f9","tid":1588973,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T05:16:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1587564\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1587564</a>"},{"pid":"c2ddfbb012c046abc911c15c156b37beb2fe7d12","tid":1588973,"uid":211935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T05:26:15.000Z","msg":"O.K<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6b96bf49f2fda15cb0b029f9ab9f7eed6f9f10b","tid":1588973,"uid":53970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T05:26:31.000Z","msg":"Noted with fuck you"}]}